      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh scent and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine condition, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
